<h1>Articles</h1>

<%# mixture of html and erb, a template system that evaluates ruby code %>
<%# that without the equal sign meaning evulate the code %>
<%# that with the equal sign meaning evaluate and return the ouput %>

Our blog has <%= Article.public_count %> articles and counting!

<ul>
	<%# accessing instance variable defined in controller %>
	<% @articles.each do |article| %>
		<%# only display if not archived %>
		<% unless article.archived? %>
			<li>
				<%= link_to article.title, article %>
			</li>
		<% end %>
	<% end %>
</ul>

